Wet hair and apply approximately 1 teaspoon (5 mL) of LOPROX Shampoo (ciclopirox shampoo)  to the scalp.  Up to 2 teaspoons (10 mL) may be used for long hair.  Lather and leave on hair and scalp for 3 minutes.  A timer may be used.  Avoid contact with eyes.  Rinse off.  Treatment should be repeated twice per week for 4 weeks, with a minimum of 3 days between applications.
If a patient with seborrheic dermatitis shows no clinical improvement after 4 weeks of treatment with LOPROX Shampoo (ciclopirox shampoo) , the diagnosis should be reviewed.
